long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
GITIL is an open-source Chrome extension that indicates the amount of days issues stayed in the same lane in Gitlab's Kanban boards.


You can find the source here : https://gitlab.com/jlengrand/gitlab-issues-time-in-lane
